#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.44:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Sagāthakapuññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "5. Overflowing Merit, With Verses"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 44. Paṭhamamahaddhanasutta → aḍḍhasuttaṃ (bj) | mahaddhana or aḍḍha 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Paṭhamamahaddhanasutta"
msgstr "44. Rich (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: mahaddhano → mahaḍḍhano (bj)
#. VAR: mahābhogo’ti → mahābhogo mahāyasoti (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn55.44:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako ‘aḍḍho mahaddhano "
"mahābhogo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a noble disciple who has four things is said to be rich, "
"affluent, and wealthy."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.44:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.4"
msgid "dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …"
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.6"
msgid ""
"ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to "
"immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.44:2.7"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako ‘aḍḍho "
"mahaddhano mahābhogo’ti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who has these four things is said to be rich, affluent, and "
"wealthy.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.44:2.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
